import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core';
import {  medecinUid } from 'src/firebaseConfig';


@Component({
  selector: 'app-app-medecin',
  templateUrl: './app-medecin.page.html',
  styleUrls: ['./app-medecin.page.scss'],
})
export class AppMedecinPage implements OnInit {

  constructor() { }

  ngOnInit() {
console.log('uidmedecin',medecinUid.uid)
  }
  async logout(){
  localStorage.clear();
  }

}


<ion-content [fullscreen]="true">
  <ion-header collapse="condense">
    <ion-toolbar>
      <ion-title size="large">app-medecin</ion-title>
    </ion-toolbar>
  </ion-header>

  <ion-grid>
    <ion-row>
      <ion-col>
    <ion-card routerLink="/patient">
      <ion-card-header>
        <ion-card-title><ion-icon name="accessibility-outline"></ion-icon>  Patient</ion-card-title>
        <ion-card-subtitle></ion-card-subtitle>
      </ion-card-header>
    
      
    </ion-card>
  </ion-col>
  </ion-row>
  <ion-row>
  <ion-col>
    <ion-card routerLink="/consultation-med">
      <ion-card-header>
        <ion-card-title><ion-icon name="file-tray-stacked-outline" ></ion-icon>  Consultation</ion-card-title>
        <ion-card-subtitle></ion-card-subtitle>
      </ion-card-header>
     
      
    </ion-card>
  </ion-col>
  </ion-row>
  <ion-row>
    <ion-col>
      <ion-card routerLink="/salle">
        <ion-card-header>
      <ion-card-title><ion-icon name="people-circle-outline"></ion-icon>  Salle d'attente</ion-card-title>
      <ion-card-subtitle></ion-card-subtitle>
    </ion-card-header>
  
    
  </ion-card>
</ion-col>
</ion-row>
<ion-row>
<ion-col>
  <ion-card routerLink="/documentmedecin">
    <ion-card-header>
      <ion-card-title><ion-icon name="folder-outline" ></ion-icon>  Documents</ion-card-title>
      <ion-card-subtitle></ion-card-subtitle>
    </ion-card-header>
   
    
  </ion-card>
</ion-col>
</ion-row>

  </ion-grid>
 
</ion-content>
<ion-footer collapse="fade">
  <ion-toolbar>
    <ion-tabs>
      <ion-tab-bar slot="bottom">
        <ion-tab-button routerLink="/app-medecin">
          <ion-icon name="home-outline" ></ion-icon>
          Home
        </ion-tab-button>
        <ion-tab-button routerLink="/calender-medecin">
          <ion-icon name="calendar-outline" ></ion-icon>
          Calendrier
        </ion-tab-button>
        <ion-tab-button routerLink="/parametre-med">
          <ion-icon name="settings-outline" ></ion-icon>
          Réglage
        </ion-tab-button>
        <ion-tab-button routerLink="/home-principal" (click)="logout()">
          <ion-icon name="log-out-outline"></ion-icon>
          Se deconnecter
        </ion-tab-button>

      </ion-tab-bar>
    </ion-tabs>
  </ion-toolbar>
</ion-footer>
